---
title: Carb Smart Cheeseburger Tofu Soup with Cheddar and Veggies
description: Packed with tofu, creamy cheese and veggies, this dish transforms drive-through deliciousness into a cozy bowl of soup! This one-pot wonder is sure to hit the spot!

